HEADWORD: Electro-dynamics
<hw>E*lec`tro-dy*nam"ics</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The phenomena of electricity in motion.</def>⟦br⟧
